I"^<h1 id="building-irida-from-source">Building IRIDA from source</h1>

<p>This document describes the necessary steps for building the IRIDA web interface from source.</p>

<ul id="markdown-toc">
  <li><a href="#building-irida-from-source" id="markdown-toc-building-irida-from-source">Building IRIDA from source</a>    <ul>
